		<blockquote class="restore">Switched over to the Bulwark (Rockman ship) to try a slightly different perspective...<br />
<br />
First couple tries BRUTAL.  The Bulwark starts with 2 Missile launchers(NO Energy weapons), 3 rockmen for crew.<br />
<br />
First try; I got creamed: starved for ammo, starved for scrap, starved for fuel.  Only made it to sector 3.  <br />
<br />
2nd try, a little better.<br />
<br />
3rd try.  Bye bye flagship.  <div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px">
<div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>Spoiler</b> for <i>playthrough</i>: <input type="button" value="Show" style="width:45px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != 'inline') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'inline'; this.value = 'Hide'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none';  this.value = 'Show'; }">
